					<div class="bio">
						<h4>Joseph Luzzi</h4>
												<p>Joseph Luzzi is professor of comparative literature at Bard College and an award-winning writer, teacher, and scholar of Italian culture. He is the author of four books and lives in New Yorkâ€™s Hudson Valley.</p>
